in_3614105\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 06, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kfj1665702629663.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kfj1665702629663.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kfj1665702629663.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kfj1665702629663\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Widget Font (\n                              Font)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Widget Font</span> (\n                                Font) property determines the font used to display the text in this widget.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__p_d109025e1_d109026e1_d109027e1\">Font<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">Font</var></p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__section_zly_51c_bxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1242645e66\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__p_d109031e1_d109032e1_d109033e1\">The default font is specified by the\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">editfont</span> definition in the application's <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span>\n        file.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__p_d109034e1_d109035e1_d109036e1\">If the specified font is larger than the available\n        space in the widget, the widget can behave unpredictably at run time. To correct this,\n        choose a smaller font or enlarge the size of the widget.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__section_pc2_lbc_bxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1242645e84\">Example: Setting in ProcScript</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__pre_iv1_nbc_bxb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$properties(FLD1) = \"Font=TahomaSmall\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__section_nyg_nbc_bxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1242645e93\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__ul_ock_4bc_bxb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__li_d42431e1_d42432e1_d42433e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kzn1665703126224.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kzn1665703126224.html\" title=\"The ucolorbox widget displays a color value, either a color name or RGB value, in a color box in a form component. Uniface provides a logical widget called ColorBox, which is mapped to ucolorbox.\">ucolorbox (ColorBox)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__li_d42434e1_d42435e1_d42436e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gzs1665702629046.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gzs1665702629046.html\" title=\"The (ucolorlist) widget displays a list of system or web colors for selection in a form component. Uniface provides a logical widget called ColorList, which is mapped to ucolorlist.\">ucolorlist (ColorList)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__li_d42437e1_d42438e1_d42439e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vmo1688449724415.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vmo1688449724415.html\" title=\"The ucombobox widget combines an input field with a drop-down list. It allows users to select one item from a previously defined list, or enter their own data instead. It is applicable only to form components. Uniface provides a logical widget called ComboBox, which is mapped to ucombobox.\">ucombobox (Combo Box)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__li_d42440e1_d42441e1_d42442e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrc1665702631553.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrc1665702631553.html\" title=\"The CommandButton is a logical widget that enables a user to initiate an action by clicking the button.\">CommandButton</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__li_d42443e1_d42444e1_d42445e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fud1688450548955.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fud1688450548955.html\" title=\"The udropdownlist widget is a field-level widget that can display a list of valid options in a list below the input field, so that the user can select one. It is applicable only to form components.\">udropdownlist (DropDownList)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__li_d42446e1_d42447e1_d42448e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"klb1688454363706.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/klb1688454363706.html\" title=\"Default logical widget for entering and displaying data in a field in a Form or Report.\">EditBox</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__li_d42449e1_d42450e1_d42451e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hta1665703126401.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hta1665703126401.html\" title=\"The uhyperlink widget is a display-only widget that acts like a hyperlink in a web page. It activates a command when the user clicks it. It can only be used in form components. Uniface provides a logical widget called Hyperlink, which is mapped to uhyperlink.\">uhyperlink (Hyperlink)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__li_d42452e1_d42453e1_d42454e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rez1688451198680.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rez1688451198680.html\" title=\"The ulistbox widget is a field-level widget that displays an open list in which one or more values can be selected. It can only be used in form components.\">ulistbox (ListBox )</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__li_d42455e1_d42456e1_d42457e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bwv1665702644903.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bwv1665702644903.html\" title=\"The umeter widget displays the value of a Numeric field on a gauge for which there is a predefined range of values marked around the outer edge. Uniface provides a logical widget called Meter, which is mapped to umeter.\">umeter (Meter)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__li_d42458e1_d42459e1_d42460e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ddd1665702643397.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ddd1665702643397.html\" title=\"The uoutputbox widget displays streaming text data. The data may come from a specified Output Channel, or be explicitly added. By default, it does not listen to any channel. Uniface provides a logical widget called OutputBox, which is mapped to uoutputbox.\">uoutputbox (OutputBox)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__li_d42461e1_d42462e1_d42463e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"svk1665702646925.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/svk1665702646925.html\" title=\"The umonthcalendar widget displays a month calendar to enable the user to select a date. Uniface provides a logical widget called MonthCalendar, which is mapped to umonthcalendar.\">(umonthcalendar) MonthCalendar</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__li_d42464e1_d42465e1_d42466e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yye1665702650577.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yye1665702650577.html\" title=\"The uradiogroup widget displays a set of mutually exclusive choices as a group of radio buttons. Uniface provides a logical widget called RadioGroup, which is mapped to uradiogroup.\">uradiogroup (RadioGroup)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__li_d42467e1_d42468e1_d42469e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qwk1688451210612.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qwk1688451210612.html\" title=\"The urtfeditbox widget is used to display and edit text as Rich Text Format (RTF), which supports formatting such as font and color attributes, text alignment, indentation, and lists. Uniface provides a logical widget called RichEditBox, which is mapped to urtfeditbox.\">urtfeditbox (RichEditBox)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__li_d42470e1_d42471e1_d42472e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lxs1665702651483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lxs1665702651483.html\" title=\"The uspinbutton widget enables the user to enter or select a numeric value by clicking a button to increase or decrease a value by a predefined interval within a predefined range. Uniface provides a logical widget called SpinButton, which is mapped to uspinbutton.\">uspinbutton (SpinButton)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__li_d42473e1_d42474e1_d42475e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bzj1665702641924.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bzj1665702641924.html\" title=\"The utab widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tab, which is mapped to utab.\">utab (Tab)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__li_d42476e1_d42477e1_d42478e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gyf1688451219719.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyf1688451219719.html\" title=\"The utabex widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. The utabex widget is highly customizable, allowing extensive control over the appearance and behavior of the tabs. Uniface provides a logical widget called TabEx, which is mapped to utabex.\">utabex (TabEx)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kfj1665702629663__li_d42479e1_d42480e1_d42481e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gge1665702634237.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gge1665702634237.html\" title=\"The utree widget enables users to view and navigate structured data as a hierarchy. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tree, which is mapped to utree.\">utree (Tree)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614105\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614105\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Widget Font ( Font) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 06, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Widget Font ( Font) The Widget Font ( Font) property determines the font used to display the text in this widget. Font = Font Description The default font is specified by the editfont definition in the application's .ini file. If the specified font is larger than the available space in the widget, the widget can behave unpredictably at run time. To correct this, choose a smaller font or enlarge the size of the widget. Example: Setting in ProcScript $properties(FLD1) = \"Font=TahomaSmall\" Copy Applies To ucolorbox (ColorBox) ucolorlist (ColorList) ucombobox (Combo Box) CommandButton udropdownlist (DropDownList) EditBox uhyperlink (Hyperlink) ulistbox (ListBox ) umeter (Meter) uoutputbox (OutputBox) (umonthcalendar) MonthCalendar uradiogroup (RadioGroup) urtfeditbox (RichEditBox) uspinbutton (SpinButton) utab (Tab) utabex (TabEx) utree (Tree) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}